pageContext.description: There seems to be a lot of tin in this implement. It shows on both sides near the edge and on one outside of wings. stop ridge is very slight. Sides of wings are faceted. Tip of one side of edge is missing.
pageContext.patina: A suggestion of patina, of light green.
